  "detailed_description": "<h1>DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368080/extras/fb3d6e6c4bf500156c45a96f4e58581c.poster.avif?t=1770319782\" width=543 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368080/extras/fb3d6e6c4bf500156c45a96f4e58581c.webm?t=1770319782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>EvoWars is a legendary MMO brawler where you evolve from a primitive warrior into a powerful Megavolution! Join millions of players in cross-platform battles where every hit matters!</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EvoWars – The Legendary Cross-Platform MMO Brawler!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💎 Steam Edition unlocks permanent perks, giving you the ultimate advantage!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Faster respawn</strong> after death  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>+30% XP</strong> for defeating enemies  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>+100% XP</strong> from collecting orbs  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>+100% Rank XP</strong> every round  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>+10% Gold</strong> earned per round  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Enhanced graphics quality</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Ad-free gameplay</strong> – pure action, no interruptions!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368080/extras/d032c650803d2aed1e369763363d8a90.poster.avif?t=1770319782\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368080/extras/d032c650803d2aed1e369763363d8a90.webm?t=1770319782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368080/extras/d032c650803d2aed1e369763363d8a90.mp4?t=1770319782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 Game Modes & Epic Battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience <strong>fast-paced cross-platform multiplayer</strong> battles with up to <strong>60 players per match</strong> across various game modes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗡️ <strong>Classic Free-for-All</strong> – Battle for supremacy in chaotic PvP arenas!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛡️ <strong>Team Modes</strong> – Cooperate with allies for tactical victories!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐲 <strong>Monster Hunt (PvE)</strong> – Join forces to defeat terrifying creatures!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>Duel</strong> – 1v1 fights for ultimate bragging rights!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🕹️ Easy to Play, Hard to Master!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>EvoWars</i> offers <strong>simple one-button combat</strong>, but mastering it requires <strong>strategy, precision, and skill</strong>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Timing your attacks, positioning yourself wisely, and outmaneuvering opponents are the keys to <strong>becoming the ultimate warrior!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368080/extras/bbbac174c04c954666044d71adf96f4c.avif?t=1770319782\" width=607 height=327 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🚀 Join the Battle Today!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're a <strong>casual player</strong> looking for quick fun or a <strong>competitive fighter</strong> aiming for the top, <i>EvoWars: New Era</i> delivers <strong>intense, action-packed battles</strong> that keep you coming back for more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Cross-platform multiplayer</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>40+ unique evolutions</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Fast, skill-based combat</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 <strong>Steam-exclusive premium rewards</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to evolve and conquer the battlefield?</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368080/extras/fb3d6e6c4bf500156c45a96f4e58581c.poster.avif?t=1770319782\" width=543 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368080/extras/fb3d6e6c4bf500156c45a96f4e58581c.webm?t=1770319782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>EvoWars is a legendary MMO brawler where you evolve from a primitive warrior into a powerful Megavolution! Join millions of players in cross-platform battles where every hit matters!</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EvoWars – The Legendary Cross-Platform MMO Brawler!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💎 Steam Edition unlocks permanent perks, giving you the ultimate advantage!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Faster respawn</strong> after death  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>+30% XP</strong> for defeating enemies  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>+100% XP</strong> from collecting orbs  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>+100% Rank XP</strong> every round  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>+10% Gold</strong> earned per round  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Enhanced graphics quality</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✔️ <strong>Ad-free gameplay</strong> – pure action, no interruptions!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368080/extras/d032c650803d2aed1e369763363d8a90.poster.avif?t=1770319782\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368080/extras/d032c650803d2aed1e369763363d